#### OMDB Movies

##### The exercise is broken down as below

- Fetch Movies using https://www.omdbapi.com/ (then, catch or async, await).
- Design a card for a movie – title, year, rated, release date, run time, poster, genre, director, actors, plot.
- Display the movie cards in responsive format.
- Sort by year
- Create a side panel (Iframe), a button on each card to view more.
- On click, display information in the iframe - all info, display all ratings, languages, full plot.
- Search within displayed movies.
- Load more – (Infinite scroll, or next page button).

##### Note
- Use arrow functions wherever possible.
- Use array methods instead of traditional loops.